SECTION 7 – SPECIAL PROJECT CREDITS & ATTRIBUTIONS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository contains various projects. Specific credits for major works are listed below to acknowledge historical contributions:

A. STARBOUND: PROJECT FR (Core Engine)
While the engine, modern dictionary structures, and scripts have been rebuilt from scratch for this project, I have chosen to include specific assets originally created by the "Starbound FR" translation team to maintain visual and community continuity.

I wish to credit the following original contributors for their foundational work:
- Project Lead: Yohann Catherine
- Steam Icon & Graphics: Mickael30HG
- Outpost & UI Image Translations: Pho3niX
- Foundation Team: Shyning, LoGeek, Phaenix, Canarder

B. OTHER PROJECTS
Credits for other games or tools included in this repository are specified within their respective sub-folders via README or metadata files.

